ygData.messageBody:
Anyone know if they've fixed the Bayle List quest yet? I'm
referring to the Freeport quest. I petition every few days about
it, but unless a GM is on, noone even knows what quest I'm talking
about, and even the server GM wasn't sure last time I petitioned.

Anyone tried to finish it recently?

And while I'm posting, in the Bloodsaber guild there is a cleric
who mentions serving the Lord of Disese (misspelled), but I
couldn't make her talk. Anyone know what the deal is there? I'm
ready to do some Qeynos quests now that I'm amiable, but I can't
find anything other than the kill paladins/drosco/clothspinner/trumpy
quests.

Xilith
